Cell["\<\
Disjoint contributions at first order containing a single two-body \
interaction vertex are 72 in total. These are distributed as follows:
i) 12 Direct diagrams dressed in the left propagator;
ii) 12 Direct diagrams dressed in the right propagator;
iii) 12 Exchange diagrams dressed in the propagator above;
iv) 12 Exchange diagrams dressed in the propagator below;
v) 12 Bogoliubov diagrams dressed in the antidiagonal propagator;
ii) 12 Bogoliubov diagrams dressed in the diagonal propagator;\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8746447846491413`*^9, 3.874644822571206*^9}, {
